mitre_attack_techniques.signature_description: Adversaries may communicate using application layer protocols to avoid detection/network filtering by blending in with existing traffic.
Adversaries may delete or modify artifacts generated within systems to remove evidence of their presence or hinder defenses.
Adversaries may delete files left behind by the actions of their intrusion activity.
Sample and/or dropped files symbols with suspicious names
Creates hidden files, links and/or directories
May try to detect the virtual machine to hinder analysis (VM artifact strings found in memory)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET INFO DYNAMIC_DNS Query to a *.accesscam .org Domain
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert dns $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"ET INFO DYNAMIC_DNS Query to a *.accesscam .org Domain"; dns.query; content:".accesscam.org"; fast_pattern; nocase; endswith; reference:url,www.dynu.com/ControlPanel/AddDDNS; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2046019; rev:2; metadata:attack_target Client_and_Server, created_at 2023_06_01, deployment Perimeter, performance_impact Low, confidence High, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2024_06_11, mitre_tactic_id TA0011, mitre_tactic_name Command_And_Control, mitre_technique_id T1568, mitre_technique_name Dynamic_Resolution;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET USER_AGENTS Go HTTP Client User-Agent
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET USER_AGENTS Go HTTP Client User-Agent"; flow:established,to_server; http.user_agent; content:"Go-http-client"; nocase; fast_pattern; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2024897; rev:3; metadata:attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2017_10_23, deployment Perimeter, confidence High, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2024_06_13;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET INFO Go-http-client User-Agent Observed Outbound
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET INFO Go-http-client User-Agent Observed Outbound"; flow:established,to_server; http.user_agent; content:"Go-http-client/"; nocase; fast_pattern; startswith; reference:url,go.dev/src/net/http/request.go#L545; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2060251; rev:1; metadata:affected_product Any, created_at 2025_02_21, signature_severity Unknown, updated_at 2025_02_21;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET INFO Observed Initial New Kind of Network (NKN) POST Request

ids_alerts.rule_msg: SSLBL: Malicious JA3 SSL-Client Fingerprint detected (CoinMiner)

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Suspicious DNS Query for IP Lookup Service APIs
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects DNS queries for IP lookup services such as "api.ipify.org" originating from a non browser process.

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Suspicious Network Connection to IP Lookup Service APIs
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects external IP address lookups by non-browser processes via services such as "api.ipify.org". This could be indicative of potential post compromise internet test activity.
